.SH NAME
ivcap - A command line tool to interact with a IVCAP deployment


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBivcap [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
A command line tool to to more conveniently interact with the
API exposed by a specific IVCAP deployment.


